Marketing executive with 20+ years experience in IT/Networking industry directing all marketing disciplines, including audience segmentation analysis, advertising, branding, AR/PR/IR, product/solution marketing, product line management, vertical solution marketing, business development and social/new media marketing. Diverse experience across large, medium and small businesses, both public and private, spanning routing, switching, and security. Frequent keynoter and thought leader / technology evangelist for notable industry events. Strong track record working closely with sales and channel organizations, including direct customer engagements and deal success. Expertise in identifying and implementing marketing solutions to improve propensity-to-buy modeling, customer acquisition, and nurturing. Greatest strengths: establishing and growing company/business market positions in hyper competitive markets, leading strategy and implementations of organizational turnarounds, building best-in-class teams and change management.



